Company Overview of Rail-Splitter Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rail-Splitter Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, other investment advisors, and endowment. It invests in public equity markets and in derivative of the United States of America. The Adviser focuses on a range of equity investment styles, but concentrates in growth stocks. Client accounts invest in all ranges on the capitalization scale, from micro-cap, through small-cap, midcap and large-cap, to mega-cap. It also invests in value stocks of companies. The firm employs fundamental analysis to make its investments. It employs bottoms-up approach to make investment decision...
Rail-Splitter Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, other investment advisors, and endowment. It invests in public equity markets and in derivative of the United States of America. The Adviser focuses on a range of equity investment styles, but concentrates in growth stocks. Client accounts invest in all ranges on the capitalization scale, from micro-cap, through small-cap, midcap and large-cap, to mega-cap. It also invests in value stocks of companies. The firm employs fundamental analysis to make its investments. It employs bottoms-up approach to make investment decisions. The firm was formerly known as CMF Capital Management, Inc. Rail-Splitter Capital Management, LLC was founded on September 1, 2002 and is based in Chicago, Illinois.
