Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
Rail-Splitter Capital Management LLC/USA operates as a hedge fund manager. The Company provides advisory services on unregistered privately pooled investment vehicles for sophisticated and institutional investors, and separately managed institutional accounts.




