Rail Splitter Capital Management








Login

Rail-Splitter Capital Management, founded in 2002 and based in Chicago, is an investment firm that manages long/short and long-only equity funds. In 2017, the Rail-Splitter Capital Management team joined RMB Capital. We continue to apply a consistent, rigorous investment approach and process that focuses on fundamental research, deep sector experience, and valuation discipline.


For more information about our investment strategies, please contact us.  
				Rail-Splitter Capital Management 
				c/o RMB Capital 
				115 South LaSalle Street, 34th floor 
				Chicago, IL 60603 
				800 601 5228 | toll-free 
www.rmbcap.com  
